vernac_cmds: Axiom initial: forall gv, initialized_globals gv |-- data 3 gv.

Definition data_ok (n: Z) (gv: globals) : mpred := !! (0 <= n <= Int.max_signed) && data_at Ews tint (Vint (Int.repr n)) (gv _LG_n) * data_at Ews (Tstruct _foo noattr) (Vint Int.one, Vint (Int.repr n)) (gv _LG_foo).
Definition data (n: Z) (gv: globals) : mpred := data_ok n gv || (!! (n=3) && data_at Ews tint (Vint (Int.repr n)) (gv _LG_n) * data_at Ews (Tstruct _foo noattr) (Vint Int.zero, Vundef) (gv _LG_foo)).

Definition initialized_globals (gv: globals) := !! (headptr (gv _LG_n)) && !! (headptr (gv _LG_foo)) && mapsto Ews tuint (offset_val 4 (gv _LG_foo)) (Vint (Int.repr 0)) * data_at Ews tuint (Vint (Int.repr 0)) (gv _LG_foo) * data_at Ews tuint (Vint (Int.repr 3)) (gv _LG_n).
Lemma initial: forall gv, initialized_globals gv |-- data 3 gv.
rewrite field_compatible_field_address by auto with field_compatible.
apply derives_trans with x; subst x.
erewrite <- mapsto_field_at by auto with field_compatible.
rewrite field_compatible_field_address by auto with field_compatible.
Definition init_spec := DECLARE _LG_init WITH n: Z, gv: globals PRE [] PROP () LOCAL(gvars gv) SEP(LG.data n gv) POST [ tvoid ] PROP() LOCAL () SEP (LG.data_ok n gv).
Definition bump_spec := DECLARE _LG_bump WITH n: Z, gv: globals PRE [] PROP (n < Int.max_signed) LOCAL(gvars gv) SEP(LG.data n gv) POST [ tvoid ] PROP() LOCAL () SEP (LG.data (n+1) gv).
Definition get_spec := DECLARE _LG_get WITH n: Z, gv: globals PRE [] PROP () LOCAL(gvars gv) SEP(LG.data n gv) POST [ tint ] PROP() LOCAL (temp ret_temp (Vint (Int.repr n))) SEP (LG.data n gv).

Definition client_spec := DECLARE _client WITH n: Z, gv: globals PRE [] PROP (n < 1000000000) LOCAL(gvars gv) SEP(LG.data n gv) POST [ tint ] PROP() LOCAL (temp ret_temp (Vint (Int.repr (n+2)))) SEP (LG.data (n+2) gv).
Definition main_spec := DECLARE _main WITH gv : globals PRE [] main_pre prog nil gv POST [ tint ] PROP() LOCAL (temp ret_temp (Vint (Int.repr 5))) SEP(TT).
Definition Gprog : funspecs := ltac:(with_library prog [ init_spec; bump_spec; get_spec; client_spec; main_spec]).
Lemma orp_if_bool: forall {A} {NA: NatDed A} (P Q: A), orp P Q = EX b: bool, if b then P else Q.
Lemma body_init: semax_body Vprog Gprog f_LG_init init_spec.
rewrite orp_if_bool; Intros b; destruct b.
Lemma body_bump: semax_body Vprog Gprog f_LG_bump bump_spec.
Lemma body_get: semax_body Vprog Gprog f_LG_get get_spec.
Lemma body_client: semax_body Vprog Gprog f_client client_spec.
Lemma body_main: semax_body Vprog Gprog f_main main_spec.
